<p>It is crucial to acknowledge that CLOs operate as managed vehicles. Given the presence of both strong and weak credits within each industry, the ability of managers to navigate these dynamics will significantly impact the overall performance of CLO tranches, especially at the equity level. Consequently, managers’ expertise in credit selection will be thoroughly tested as they strive to deliver favorable results in this challenging landscape.</p>



